r />\n最主要香港租金太貴，搞到又要限時，又坐得逼，食物又偷工減料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n椰子雞先大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 落勁撚多工業椰子粉</blockquote><br />\n我食果間係有人check過係用真椰青😎"},{"pid":"cc3800ee507a9516509f22b8589a860005e0661d","tid":134564,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T08:51:02.000Z","msg":"深圳萬象城地牢間超市，真係去到邊都幾條友企係度招呼你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea536fdc3ac7400703d7748e6f7922fad6b8ab22","tid":134564,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T08:54:35.000Z","msg":"你都戇鳩，西餐日餐深圳根本無師傅識煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52968547d0a73d1a40c8dabe8e2060f48d3c6e0c","tid":134564,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T08:56:36.000Z","msg":"講真，深食野個價真係泊得住香港，但好味程度就唔夠香港黎！"},{"pid":"e2493f875c15ed4a17fecd1a49a4ebfa0ef1c45f","tid":134564,"uid":51158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T12:20:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>'講食物質素，大陸中高檔餐廳基本都唔會用黑心材料，淨係八大菜系加埋新派fusion野大把揀'<br />\n<br />\n見到依句笑咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主唔好咁天真啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你係鬼國連飲啖水/抖啖氣都有毒啦<br />\n野食種類更加唔洗講，你講到香港無野食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOn9仔，香港啲水都係大陸黎咋，香港仲要再加埋氟化物，真係唔會好過大陸好多。同埋我講緊深圳。</blockquote><br />\n我屌你老母啦，如果大陸水係乾淨既，唔撚洗拎去過濾，唔洗加氟化物啦，直接俾你飲好唔撚好？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/search?client=ms-android-samsung&amp;ei=ncayWIXYIoux8wWzlozgBQ&amp;q=東江水水質&amp;oq=東江水&amp;gs_l=mobile-gws-serp.1.2.0l5.2765.5340.0.6963.8.7.0.1.1.0.230.887.0j5j1.6.0....0...1c.1j4.64.mobile-gws-serp..2.6.781.3..41j0i131k1.EjpRFwXttaA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=h