ad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你係鬼國連飲啖水/抖啖氣都有毒啦<br />\n野食種類更加唔洗講，你講到香港無野食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOn9仔，香港啲水都係大陸黎咋，香港仲要再加埋氟化物，真係唔會好過大陸好多。同埋我講緊深圳。</blockquote><br />\n我屌你老母啦，如果大陸水係乾淨既，唔撚洗拎去過濾，唔洗加氟化物啦，直接俾你飲好唔撚好？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/search?client=ms-android-samsung&amp;ei=ncayWIXYIoux8wWzlozgBQ&amp;q=東江水水質&amp;oq=東江水&amp;gs_l=mobile-gws-serp.1.2.0l5.2765.5340.0.6963.8.7.0.1.1.0.230.887.0j5j1.6.0....0...1c.1j4.64.mobile-gws-serp..2.6.781.3..41j0i131k1.EjpRFwXttaA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fsearch%3Fclient%3Dms-android-samsung%26ei%3DncayWIXYIoux8wWzlozgBQ%26q%3D%E6%9D%B1%E6%B1%9F%E6%B0%B4%E6%B0%B4%E8%B3%AA%26oq%3D%E6%9D%B1%E6%B1%9F%E6%B0%B4%26gs_l%3Dmobile-gws-serp.1.2.0l5.2765.5340.0.6963.8.7.0.1.1.0.230.887.0j5j1.6.0....0...1c.1j4.64.mobile-gws-serp..2.6.781.3..41j0i131k1.EjpRFwXttaA&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4567b261\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/search?client=ms-android-samsung&amp;ei=ncayWIXYIoux8wWzlozgBQ&amp;q=東江水水質&amp;oq=東江水&amp;gs_l=mobile-gws-serp.1.2.0l5.2765.5340.0.6963.8.7.0.1.1.0.230.887.0j5j1.6.0....0...1c.1j4.64.mobile-gws-serp..2.6.781.3..41j0i131k1.EjpRFwXttaA</a><br />\ngoogle 埋你睇啊，柒頭</blockquote><br />\n柒頭，自己google下氟化物係乜撚野黎先衝出黎柒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a7f47ed75375d1ea6ad8bdf05560adf6365874","tid":134564,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T14:06:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>'講食物質素，大陸中高檔餐廳基本都唔會用黑心材料，淨係八大菜系加埋新派fusion野大把揀'<br />\n<br />\n見到依句笑咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主唔好咁天真啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你係鬼國連飲啖水/抖啖氣都有毒啦<br />\n野食種類更加唔洗講，你講到香港無野食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h