企係度招呼你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n煩撚到仆街<br />\n買日用品自己唔識買咩，係咁sell<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有服務好過冇</blockquote><br />\n我寧願無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ecf6569db6431025cdc42662cd473722259b728","tid":134564,"uid":26071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T15:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食過深圳華僑州際 自助餐可以用垃圾黎形容<br />\n<br />\n但有d餐廳 200蚊左右 真心好食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係大陸千祈唔好食自助餐<br />\n點夠班蝗一次過拎一座山嘢食<br />\n加上生蠔魚生都係入口嘢<br />\n款式同質素都同香港有一定落差<br />\n<br />\n反而真係200蚊去間中高檔嘅餐廳食好過<br />\n嗰堆餐廳打貪前隨時貴過香港<br />\n係依家班貪官唔敢出來幫襯先局住減價"},{"pid":"d3ec6d92a27d686902c56dbb2de866f961900c5f","tid":134564,"uid":1274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T15:59:21.000Z","msg":"樓主，你講得啱！"},{"pid":"8f2a009ef4c39eb9f8109efc8146f6418a323c87","tid":134564,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T16:03:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>'講食物質素，大陸中高檔餐廳基本都唔會用黑心材料，淨係八大菜系加埋新派fusion野大把揀'<br />\n<br />\n見到依句笑咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主唔好咁天真啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你係鬼國連飲啖水/抖啖氣都有毒啦<br />\n野食種類更加唔洗講，你講到香港無野食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOn9仔，香港啲水都係大陸黎咋，香港仲要再加埋氟化物，真係唔會好過大陸好多。同埋我講緊深圳。</blockquote><br />\n我屌你老母啦，如果大陸水係乾淨既，唔撚洗拎去過濾，唔洗加氟化物啦，直接俾你飲好唔撚好？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/search?client=ms-android-samsung&amp;ei=ncayWIXYIoux8wWzlozgBQ&amp;q=東江水水質&amp;oq=東江水&amp;gs_l=mobile-gws-serp.1.2.0l5.2765.5340.0.6963.8.7.0.1.1.0.230.887.0j5j1.6.0....0...1c.1j4.64.mobile-gws-serp..2.6.781.3..41j0i131k1.EjpRFwXttaA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fsearch%3Fclient%3Dms-android-samsung%26ei%3DncayWIXYIoux8wWzlozgBQ%26q%3D%E6%9D%B1%E6%B1%9F%E6%B0%B4%E6%B0%B4%E8%B3%AA%26oq%3D%E6%9D%B1%E6%B1%9F%E6%B0%B4%26gs_l%3Dmobile-gws-serp.1.2.0l5.2765.5340.0.6963.8.7.0.1.1.0.230.887.0j5j1.6.0....0...1c.1j4.64.mobile-gws-serp..2.6.781.3..41j0i131k1.EjpRFwXttaA&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4567b261\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/search?client=ms-android-samsung&amp;ei=ncayWIXYIoux8wWzlozgBQ&amp;q=東江水水質&amp;oq=東江水&amp;gs_l=mobile-gws-serp.1.2.0l5.2765.5340.0.6963.8.7.0.1.1.0.230.887.0j5j1.6.0....0...1c.1j4.64.mobile-gws-serp..2.6.781.3..41j0i131k1.EjpRFwXttaA</a><br />\ngoogle 埋你睇啊，柒頭</blockquote><br />\n仲有你唔係以為大陸人會唔將水過濾同消毒就咁拎黎用呀？<br />\n<br />\n盲反都有少少常識啦</blockquote><br />\n咁你唔好用牙膏，同埋番大陸飲水啦</blockquote><br />\n又追柒....牙膏本身係無加氟化物囉"},{"pid":"acae80b2a0ce710142fb4e327fafd21f9851420e","tid":134564,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T17:16:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我支持樓主<br />\n上年有半年係大陸做野<br />\n<br />\n200幾既放日本放題=香港500幾既質素<br />\n仲有清酒梅酒任飲</blockquote><br />\n邊間？深圳？我都好鍾意返去食野，雖然老實講平均質素真係麻麻，可能因為人地鋪租平易開到鋪頭，但如果識食既真係有好多平靚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 百幾二百蚊可以食到香港五六百既質素</blockquote><br />\n我真係唔撚識食喇<br />\n上次全公司喺深圳食buffet lunch<br />\n200蚊一個人，唔好食，冇野食到個個喺度打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b360ee6b23477150d8e10130845f144b913e2d37","tid":134564,"uid":64571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T18:47:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我支持樓主<br />\n上年有半年係大陸做野<br />\n<br />\n200幾既放日本放題=香港500幾既質素<br />\n仲有清酒梅酒任飲</blockquote><br />\n邊間？深圳？我都好鍾意返去食野，雖然老實講平均質素真係麻麻，可能因為人地鋪租平易開到鋪頭，但如果識食既真係有好多平靚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 百幾二百蚊可以食到香港五六百既質素</blockquote><br />